---
title: Chicken & Creamy Peppercorn Sauce with Potato Mash & Greens
description: One taste of this creamy peppercorn sauce and you'll want to pour it over everything! The gentle warming heat melds beautifully with the decadent cream for a rich and tasty addition to this simple meal. Add a smooth potato mash and nutty greens for a weeknight dinner that's better than most!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-creamy-peppercorn-sauce-e9f0acf4.jpg
